Middle management is collapsing — and Gen Z is leading the charge with a new workplace trend called conscious unbossing. Translation? “No thanks, I don’t want your stress sandwich promotion with a side of burnout.”

In this video, I break down the latest cringe buzzword that actually… kinda makes sense.
